Date: Wed, 17 Nov 2021 21:12:18 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 24/78] Platform/Sgi: Add fdtlib and PcdFfaEnable

Enable PcdFfaEnable flag for StandaloneMm on rdn2 platform.
Add fdtlib, needed for StandaloneMm DTS parsing.

Signed-off-by: Sayanta Pattanayak <sayanta.pattanayak@arm.com>
Change-Id: I7553645e35a06225a2d712ed9312095b32524bad
Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
---
 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/PlatformStandaloneMm2.dsc            | 9 +++++++++
 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/RdN2/RdN2.dsc                        | 5 +++++
 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/RdN2Cfg1/RdN2Cfg1.dsc                | 5 +++++
